cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a neural network model for recognizing human actions in videos, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The model also involves the use of recurrent neural networks, which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories. Finally, the paper evaluates the model's performance on human action video datasets, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
